I’m Janith Wanniarachchi, a final year undergraduate finishing my
BSc. in Statistics (Hons.) degree from the University of Sri
Jayewardenepura, a leading government University situated in Colombo and
ranked as the 2bd in the country. Currently my Statistics GPA is at
3.8/4.0 and my overall GPA is at 3.81/4.0, with two
subjects(Econometrics, Research) awaiting results.
My research interests are mainly in data visualization, time series
forecasting, bayesian inference and interpretable machine learning. On
this website you will find some of my work and interests in statistics
and creative writing.
